  "detailed_description": "Fair free to play collectible card game in dark fantasy setting.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/679200/extras/e90e67116dcb8430492a5075425c095c.avif?t=1629998735\" width=616 height=198 /></span><br><br><i>\"On the edge of the world, on the very border with the Abyss, mysterious masters of the Forbidden Game are looking for new disciples who could stand on their side in an endless game of existence.\"</i><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Almost every card has a unique ability;<br></li><li>Over 100 cards in the first set;<br></li><li>Short game sessions (about 5 to 10 minutes);<br></li><li>Player appearance customization;<br></li><li>All content is available via in-game currency;<br><i>\"We giveaway boosters and cards for free, this is <strong>Not</strong> a \"pay2win\" model. Our monetization goal is to sell appearance, that has no impact on gameplay.\"</i><br></li><li>Built-in tournament and ladder systems;<br></li><li>Unique game mechanics;</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Fair free to play collectible card game in dark fantasy setting.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/679200/extras/e90e67116dcb8430492a5075425c095c.avif?t=1629998735\" width=616 height=198 /></span><br><br><i>\"On the edge of the world, on the very border with the Abyss, mysterious masters of the Forbidden Game are looking for new disciples who could stand on their side in an endless game of existence.\"</i><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Almost every card has a unique ability;<br></li><li>Over 100 cards in the first set;<br></li><li>Short game sessions (about 5 to 10 minutes);<br></li><li>Player appearance customization;<br></li><li>All content is available via in-game currency;<br><i>\"We giveaway boosters and cards for free, this is <strong>Not</strong> a \"pay2win\" model. Our monetization goal is to sell appearance, that has no impact on gameplay.\"</i><br></li><li>Built-in tournament and ladder systems;<br></li><li>Unique game mechanics;</li></ul>",
